::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 503051205: Config/Level/Mission/5030510/Act/Act503051205.json-->
::'''Uma:''' ...Hm? Now that's interesting, the story of these monsters would make great news articles.
::'''Uma:''' Not only can the Dreamjolt Troupe interact with humans, they even offer performances! It seems that the legendary drinksmith is indeed an impressive woman. I should invite her for a special feature interview on my program.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Chat)
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503051274-->
::----
:<pre>{
