::'''Uma:''' Let me think... I probably don't have time but, speak quickly, I snuck out here to have a look around.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I want to know your thoughts on Siobhan.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503051276-->
:::'''Uma:''' Siobhan? That's the name of the mysterious drinksmith, correct? I've heard a number of things about her.
:::'''Uma:''' Her background is complicated, if you want to know the specifics then you should ask around for yourself. Either way, I know that she holds a lot of renown within The Family... The Iris Family, if I remember rightly...? You cannot tell anyone that you heard this from me.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I want to know what you think about me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503051279-->
:::'''Uma:''' Are you the new drinksmith here? I hear that it's you that has been looking after those monsters lately? I hear it's going well, and they trust you a lot, that they are willing to share their thoughts with you. It seems you're quite the adept communicator.
:::'''Uma:''' I will send someone to write a report on what I've seen here and let our viewers know. Keep an eye on the TV!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
